Luxe Places International Realty, Mendocino Coast Branch

data.description: Spectacular home in the heart of downtown Fort Bragg. This 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath house has a large family room, bonus room with half bath, and three spacious bedrooms with views of the ocean. The giant backyard lot has a finished Tuff Shed with bathroom and electricity. Gardens, lush lawn, fruit trees, large wood deck, built in tool shed complete this gorgeous backyard with so much potential. Close to downtown dining, shopping, and Skunk Train. Within a mile of Glass Beach, and beach access. Complete your dream of living in Mendocino County with this one of kind home, in move in ready condition.
